    • Student

      public Student​(java.lang.String userId, java.lang.String name, java.lang.String gender, java.lang.String nationality, java.lang.String email, java.lang.String matricNo, java.time.LocalDateTime[] accessPeriod, java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String> courses, java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String> waitlist) throws MissingParametersException
      Constructor
      Parameters:
      userId - String identifier for student user. Must be unique among all users
      name - Name of student user
      gender - Gender of student user
      nationality - Nationality of student user
      email - Email address for student
      matricNo - Matriculation number for student user. Must be unique among all students
      accessPeriod - Access period for student user
      courses - Courses taken by student. Hashmap mapping course codes to indexes
      waitlist - Waitlist of student. Hashmap mapping course codes to indexes
      Throws:
      MissingParametersException - Thrown if any above fields are null
